data.description: Incredible Dewey Beach Home with 180' View! Solid 2-bedroom home with roughed in walk out basement, stands on nearly 1/3 acre of gently sloping land overlooking Cornet Bay, Deception Pass Park and the Olympic Mountains. Main floor includes large kitchen (w/2 pantries), living, dining, and spacious guest room/office. Primary Suite with new flooring has full bath and walk in closet and second closet. Attached 2 car garage and HUGE (760 +/- sqft RV/Boat/workshop with separate entrance on the lower level. Brand New Roof and Gutters. Ample opportunity to customize or expand (3 Bd septic) according to your personal vision and the location is close to beaches, parks and yet minutes to town.
